quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  11,118,"Walaw shaa rabbuka lajaAAala annasaommatan wahidatan wala yazaloonamukhtalifeen"
  11,119,"Illa man rahima rabbuka walithalikakhalaqahum watammat kalimatu rabbika laamlaanna jahannama minaaljinnati wannasi ajmaAAeen"
  11,120,"Wakullan naqussu AAalayka min anba-iarrusuli ma nuthabbitu bihi fu-adaka wajaakafee hathihi alhaqqu wamawAAithatun wathikralilmu/mineen"
  11,121,"Waqul lillatheena layu/minoona iAAmaloo AAala makanatikum innaAAamiloon"
  11,122,"Wantathiroo innamuntathiroon"
  11,123,"Walillahi ghaybu assamawatiwal-ardi wa-ilayhi yurjaAAu al-amru kulluhu faAAbudhuwatawakkal AAalayhi wama rabbuka bighafilin AAammataAAmaloon"
  12,1,"Alif-lam-ra tilka ayatualkitabi almubeen"
  12,2,"Inna anzalnahu qur-ananAAarabiyyan laAAallakum taAAqiloon"
  12,3,"Nahnu naqussu AAalayka ahsanaalqasasi bima awhayna ilayka hathaalqur-ana wa-in kunta min qablihi lamina alghafileen"
  12,4,"Ith qala yoosufu li-abeehi yaabati innee raaytu ahada AAashara kawkaban washshamsawalqamara raaytuhum lee sajideen"
